author: rcmatthews
msg: Fixtures are now just POJOs that have an install method in them.  Access to special functionality is provided by two helpers: FixtureServices and FixtureFactoryAndRepository.  Both of these are immediately available from the abstract fixture class AbstractFixture.
Outside of the app lib, within the framework is a special abstract fixture class (PerspectiveFixture) for creating NO's Perspectives.
